\fB\-M\fR, \fB\-\-monitors\fR [\fIMONITOR_SEL\fR]
.RS 4
List the IDs (or names) of the matching monitors\&.
.RE
.PP
\fB\-T\fR, \fB\-\-tree\fR
.RS 4
Print a JSON representation of the matching item\&.
.RE
